  "contenu": [
    {
      "id": "e5ed0fb4-6bd5-4ffa-91a7-663c21c5dfd8",
      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soient $z_0,z_1,\\dots,z_n \\in \\C$ tels que :\n$\\forall\\ P \\in \\C_{n-1}[X]$, on a $P(z_0) = \\frac {P(z_1) +\\dots+ P(z_n)}n$.\n\\\\\nOn note $\\Phi(X) = \\prod_{i=1}^n (X-z_i)$.",
        "html": "<p>Soient <span class=\"math inline\">\\(z_0,z_1,\\dots,z_n \\in \\C\\)</span> tels que : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\forall\\ P \\in \\C_{n-1}[X]\\)</span>, on a <span class=\"math inline\">\\(P(z_0) = \\frac {P(z_1) +\\dots+ P(z_n)}n\\)</span>.<br />\nOn note <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\Phi(X) = \\prod_{i=1}^n (X-z_i)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "5960ee20-71dc-466b-b0e1-9c4251334042",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer $\\frac {\\Phi(z_0)}{z_0-z_k}$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac {\\Phi(z_0)}{z_0-z_k}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "3e8bdf0e-7f55-4b51-ab0e-4517e4e90707",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$P = \\frac \\Phi{X-z_k}  \\Rightarrow \n     \\frac {\\Phi(z_0)}{z_0-z_k}  = \\frac {\\Phi'(z_k)}n$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(P = \\frac \\Phi{X-z_k}  \\Rightarrow \n     \\frac {\\Phi(z_0)}{z_0-z_k}  = \\frac {\\Phi&#39;(z_k)}n\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "09a6ccd3-999c-4263-a775-566258a479f8",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "En d{\\'e}duire que $\\Phi(X) = \\frac {(X-z_0)\\Phi'(X)}n + \\Phi(z_0)$.",
        "html": "<p>En d<span>é</span>duire que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\Phi(X) = \\frac {(X-z_0)\\Phi&#39;(X)}n + \\Phi(z_0)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba2c587-b71e-4147-82bd-b48afbd35477",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Les deux membres sont {\\'e}gaux en $z_0,\\dots,z_n$.",
        "html": "<p>Les deux membres sont <span>é</span>gaux en <span class=\"math inline\">\\(z_0,\\dots,z_n\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "21e233ac-b9f9-4e1d-aa2a-18e8d5fe1532",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "D{\\'e}montrer que $z_1,\\dots,z_n$ sont les sommets d'un polygone r{\\'e}gulier de centre\n     $z_0$.",
        "html": "<p>D<span>é</span>montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(z_1,\\dots,z_n\\)</span> sont les sommets d’un polygone r<span>é</span>gulier de centre <span class=\"math inline\">\\(z_0\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "16e37adc-a8bb-4b16-b67c-a5fe066617b3",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "D{\\'e}composer $\\Phi$ sur la base $\\bigl((X-z_0)^k\\bigr)$.",
        "html": "<p>D<span>é</span>composer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\Phi\\)</span> sur la base <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\bigl((X-z_0)^k\\bigr)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "d71005ba-31fd-4ebf-ad39-51c1f53ef3c0",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "R{\\'e}ciproque ?",
        "html": "<p>R<span>é</span>ciproque ?</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "e07d0b7c-6d80-4ac1-9632-a3bed0dbcfc8",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\sum_k e^{2ikp/n} = 0$ pour $p < n  \\Rightarrow $ OK.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sum_k e^{2ikp/n} = 0\\)</span> pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\(p &lt; n  \\Rightarrow\\)</span> OK.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
}